# QODANA_READ_SPACE_PACKAGES_TOKEN (compose.private.yaml). Pins in docs/phase-0-decisions.md; EnvContractTest
# asserts byte-identity for QD_VERSION/QD_BUILD + the feed/verify/eap contract.
